    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_9215499251287787370.png",
                "id": "talent26598",
                "key": "Dawnstar Piercer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dawnstar Piercer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> dan memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Icy Quill</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Icy Quill</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> yang diakibatkan oleh Karaktermu akan mengakibatkan DMG +1. (Termasuk DMG reaksi Swirl dengan campuran <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> yang dipicu oleh Karakter)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/af48cc3ce2404a2ad32b4632074daafc_8684398082788604554.png",
                "id": "talent60080",
                "key": "Spring Spirit Summoning",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Spring Spirit Summoning"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Talisman Spirit</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/0af9611ff900342f560004bd85d6e766_3232219401012446831.png",
                "id": "talent70016",
                "key": "Divine Maiden's Deliverance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Divine Maiden's Deliverance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Panggilan ini berada dalam arena:</span> <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> dan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> yang diterima Karakter lawan +1.</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8384224853023107260.png",
                "id": "talent47383",
                "key": "Talisman Spirit",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/0729bd2530214665f6a30676963e3d6f_145815749339351356.png",
                "title": "Talisman Spirit"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5763538243005354359.png",
                "id": "talent57083",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4624758862963567197.png",
